-------------------------------------------------
Installation and Configuration of SSID
-------------------------------------------------

------------
Installation
------------

1) Install MySQL, Apache, Ruby (1.8.7), Rails (2.3) and rake (0.9.2.2) 
1) Download SSID from the GitHub repository:
	https://github.com/WING-NUS/SSID

2) Download the following softwares:
	2.1) MySQL Connector/J version 5.1.13 from
		http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/
	     And put the downloaded file into the following directories:
		java/programs/lib
		java/PlagiarismDetection/lib    (for recompiling purpose
						only)
		java/DBSCAN/lib (for recompiling purpose only)

	2.2) Download "popup-window.js" from 
		http://www.php-development.ru/java 
scripts/popup-window.php
	     And put the file into
		public/javascripts


-------------
Configuration
-------------

1) Copy config/database/database.yml.template to
	config/database/database.yml

2) Modify database.yml with your database settings

3) Execute the following command in the root directory of SSID:
	rake db:migrate RAILS_ENV="production"

4) Configure Apache to serve web requests to SSID


